---

## Business Details (must be respected in every section of the output):
- Business Name: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['busness name'] }}
- Market Type: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['market type'] }}
- Country: {{ $('On form submission').item.json.country }}
- Budget: {{ $('On form submission').item.json.budget }}
- Goal: {{ $('On form submission').item.json.goal }}

---

## Original Marketing Plan (to be corrected):
{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output }}

---

## Issues to Fix:
{{ $('Code in JavaScript1').item.json.issues }}

---

## Instructions:
- Address every single issue listed above — none should be left unresolved.
- Every section must remain fully aligned with the business details above.
- Use the correct local currency for {{ $('On form submission').item.json.country }}  for all monetary values.
- Tailor all channels, content tone, and ad splits specifically to {{ $('On form submission').item.json.country }}  and {{ $('On form submission').item.json['market type'] }}.
- Preserve all parts of the original plan that are correct and do not relate to any listed issue.
- Do not mention the issues or the original version anywhere in your output.
- Output only the final, polished marketing plan using the exact format defined in your system instructions.

